text: Margit Tóth (27 October 1961 – 18 December 2016) was a Hungarian artistic gymnast. She competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics. Born in Dunaújváros in 1961, Tóth died in 2016 at the age of 55. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1961 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Hungarian female artistic gymnasts Category:People from Dunaújváros
